    {
      "text": "Disney's The Lion King 1½ (known as Disney's The Lion King outside North America) is a 2003 platform game based on the 2004 animated film of the same name. It was developed by Vicarious Visions and published by Disney Interactive, whilst THQ distributed the game in Europe. The game was released worldwide for Game Boy Advance on October 7, 2003 (the same day the original film came to DVD for the first time), 4 months before the film came out.",
